### 1.2 wheel (QQQ/NVDA/SMH and other .csv/profile-enabled symbols)

- Primary objective: maximize wheel-cycle expected outcome over time (CSP -> CC -> CSP), with ownership flexibility.
- Assignment stance: assignment is allowed; post-assignment lane management and follow-on CC selection are first-class behaviors.
- Implementation context: multiple profiles per strategy and multiple algorithms can emit concurrent candidates per symbol.

