## 3. Constraints and Design Principles

- Local-first deterministic system: no cloud requirement for core run loop.
- Manual execution model: engine emits recommendations/signals; user executes at brokerage.
- Externalized operational artifacts: DB/env/manual CSVs live outside repo root via keys-root indirection.
- SQLite is the canonical operational state store with schema governance/migrations.
- Policy-driven runtime behavior: symbols, profile enablement, and many constraints come from strategy policy JSON.
- Safety and auditability over automation: stable lineage, repeatable reruns, and explicit routing semantics are prioritized.

