## 4. Current Architecture (5k ft)

### 4.1 End-to-end flow

1. Ingest quote/greek inputs for profile-enabled symbols and applicable expirations.
2. Load current manual position and manual execution inputs (CSV contracts).
3. Evaluate strategy rules per symbol, per algorithm, and per enabled profile.
4. Apply deterministic ordering and lifecycle routing context.
5. Persist signals, lifecycle/state data, and related metadata in SQLite.
6. Render operator console output (including NEWwheel/OPENwheel distinctions and optional score/premium suffixes-- per following screenshot).
7. Operator reviews output and executes manually; next run ingests resulting executions and advances lane state.

