## 5. Strategy Logic at a Glance

### 5.1 holdWrite_cc (MSFT)

- Intent: conservative premium collection with assignment-risk suppression.
- Profile constraints govern symbol eligibility and strike/expiration filtering.
- Ex-dividend logic remains a high-priority risk path for early assignment management.
- AlgoD and AlgoGplus both operate, but with different selection/scoring style.

